                <h1>Breaking all the rules</h1>
                
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/karen-hauptman">Karen Hauptman</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
